<p>Over: The interview comes after Kyly and Michael announced their $40million divorce after seven years of marriage. Kyly and Michael had been separated for five months, but only revealed their split in a surprise announcement on February 12</p>

<p>Kyly and Michael had been separated for five months, but only revealed their split in a surprise announcement on February 12.   </p>

<p>The Clarkes, who were high-school sweethearts, have said the 'amicable' decision to separate was 'the best course' for their daughter Kelsey Lee.</p>

<p>Michael and Kyly have reportedly already agreed terms on their divorce - as well as arrangements to co-parent their daughter - without going through the courts. </p>

<p>After months of speculation, Michael went public with his romance with fashion designer Pip Edwards in July. </p>

<p>New flame: After months of speculation, Michael went public with his romance with fashion designer Pip Edwards in July. Both pictured </p>

<p>The pair enjoyed a vacation in Noosa with Pip, 40, and their children from previous relationships, Kelsey Lee Clarke and 13-year-old Justice Single.</p>

<p>The couple documented their trip on Instagram, marking the first time they have publicly acknowledged their relationship.</p>

<p>They began dating after Michael's split from Kyly last year, but their romance didn't make headlines until February, when the Clarkes publicly announced their separation. </p>

